text: Nikolina Kursar (5 August 1991) is a Norwegian taekwondo practitioner. She competed at the 2009 and 2011 World Taekwondo Championships. She won a bronze medal in welterweight at the 2009 World Taekwondo Championships in Copenhagen. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1991 births Category:Living people Category:Norwegian female taekwondo practitioners Category:World Taekwondo Championships medalists
